snippet.title: TrackMaster Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
After 1 year of development, and 6 months on itch.io, TrackMaster: Free For All Motorsport enters early access phase!

This means the game is now availble for you to buy it, and from now on, the development cycle will be consistent, with new vehicles, tracks and game modes being added at a regular basis. 

Play and buy the game at
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1536740/TrackMaster_Free_For_All_Motorsport/
https://trackmaster.itch.io/trackmaster-free-for-all-motorsport

Follow the game:
https://twitter.com/TrackmasterGame
https://www.reddit.com/r/TrackMasterFreeForAll/

Music:
Motherlode by Kevin MacLeod
Link: https://incompetech.filmmusic.io/song/4083-motherlode
License: https://filmmusic.io/standard-license

#Godot #RacingGame #MonsterTruck #Drift #GodotVehicle
